  12,15,"Enti ŒµberŒµ a wÕª‚Äôde no kÕªeŒµ na wÕªn nyinaa gye too mu sŒµ wÕª‚Äôde no bŒµto abura amena (donkodonko) no mu no, Ye‚Äôyi kyerŒµŒµ no (Yosef) sŒµ: ‚Äú(Nyame pŒµ a daakye bi) nokorŒµ sŒµ, wobŒµbÕª wÕªn, wÕªn saa asŒµm yi ho amaneŒµ wÕª aberŒµ a (saa berŒµ no) wÕª‚Äônnhu (sŒµ wone Yosef)"
